(300, 1, '2021-12-04 08:55:42', '2021-12-04 08:55:42', '<h2>c im t ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11, 1 ngn ng dn ng:</h2>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_3271\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3271\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3271\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"></figcaption></figure>\r\n<h3>Sn xut trn dy chuyn Italia, thit k hin i sang trng:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 sn xut trn dy chuyn hin i ca Italia.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tiu chun cht lng<strong>ISO 9001:2015</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>C thit k sang trng hin i, nh gn tit kim khng gian. D dng bi tr cng thit k tng th cn phng ni t t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>My nn cht lng cao cho  lnh su:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 s dng my nn cht lng cao, vn hnh m bn b trong thi gian di. T lm lnh nhanh xung di m 18oC (-18oC) v tit kim in.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Dn lnh ng ng</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng 252L HCF 516S11 s dng dn lnh bng ng ng nguyn cht lm lnh nhanh siu bn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Lp cch nhit dy:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lp cch nhit Polyurethane ca T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 dy 50mm n 60mmm cch nhit hiu qu, chng tht thot nhit, gip t vn hnh an ton trong thi gian di v tit kim in. S dng cht tr n th h mi Cylopentane trong lp cch nhit gip cch an ton cho thc phm ng lnh trong t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Mi cht lnh (gas) R600a:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng Ha Pht HCF 516S11 s dng mi cht lm lnh l Gas R600a gip tit kim ti 40% in nng so vi cc loi Gas khc bi n yu cu mt p xut ngng thp. Thm vo  n cng bo v sc khe ngi s dng v khng gy nh hng ti mi trng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11, 1 ngn ng dn ng c vt liu cu to cao cp:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lng trong T ng Ha Pht HCF 516S11 c lm bng nhm nhn cao cp, tng  bn v kh nng truyn nhit v gim mc  bm tuyt bn trong t.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thn v cnh t c lm bng thp dy, b mt ph sn tnh in cao cp bng p v bn, trnh han g trong sut qu trnh s dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Dong cnh t dng gi:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Giong cnh t ng 252L HCF 516S11 c thit k dng gi, c th tho ra gip v sinh giong d dng v nng cao tui th ca t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Kha an ton chc chn:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cnh t ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 thit k c kha chc chn. An ton cho gia nh c tr nh hay trnh mt  cho ca hng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Ca knh la cng lc:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bn di ca trn ki vali, t ng Ha Pht HCF 516S11 trang b ca knh la bng knh cng lc<strong>duy nht ch c ti t ng Ha Pht.</strong>Gip d dng quan st bn trong t v la chn sn phm cn ly ra m khng cn m tung c cnh. Gip gim thiu tht thot nhit nng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Nt iu khin d dng quan st v vn hnh</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 b tr nt iu chnh nhit  v cc n bo ngun v hot ng (power/ operqation) nm pha chn t bn ngoi. Gip d dng quan st v vn hnh theo mong mun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Gi treo tng tnh linh hot:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng 252L HCF 516S11 Thit k gi treo tng tnh linh hot trong b tr sp xp  bn trong t..</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>L thot nc</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>L thot nc bn t ng Ha Pht HCF 516S11 trong dn ra ng thi pha sau t gip vic x tuyt v sinh lau chi t d dng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Chn bnh xe chu lc:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11 c thit k vi 4 chn bnh xe chu lc gip d dng di chuyn, b tr sp xp v tr lp t t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Bo hnh di nht th trng</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T ng HCF 516S11 c thi hn bo hnh ln n<strong>30 thng</strong>di nht trn th trng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_3272\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3272\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3272\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"></figcaption></figure>\r\n<h2><strong>Thng s k thut t ng Ha Pht 252L HCF 516S11, 1 ngn ng dn ng:</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Model: HCF 516S11</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dung tch s dng</strong>: 252 lt</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi: 1 ngn, 1 ch  ( ng )</li>\r\n 	<li>Dn lnh: ng</li>\r\n 	<li>Cng sut: 123 W</li>\r\n 	<li>Kch thc ( R x S x C ): 1080 x 610 x 885 (mm)</li>\r\n 	<li>Trng lng: 45 Kg</li>\r\n 	<li>Gas: R600a</li>\r\n 	<li>Ti